Package: r2dii.ggplot
Title: Creates standard 2DII plots using ggplot
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Monika",
           family = "Furdyna",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "monika.furdyna@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package allows the user to create standardized 2DII graphis, like trajectory charts or technology mix charts and outputs them as ggplot objects. It also contains data processing functions that prepare the standard bank's data to be an input for the plotting functions.
